Tosin Adeloye (amuru na ọnwa 7 Februarị nke afọ  1996) bu onye oso oso Naijiria
Ọ gbara asọmpi mita 400 na asọmpi egwuregwu ụwa nke afọ 2015 na Beijing, China
Adeloye nwalere ihe ọma maka anabolic steroid Metenolone na National Sports Festival na Lagos na Disemba 2012, mgbe ọ dị afọ 16, ma mesịa machibido ya egwuregwu afọ abụọ
Ọ natara mmachibido iwu nke abụọ maka afọ asatọ ka ule ọzọ dara na 2016
